summary:
Moumouni has an extensive theoretical background and he specialized in several fields: public law, corporate law, international trade law and sustainable development. In both the Netherlands and Ivory Coast he built a diverse career.
Moumouni now brings his knowledge and experience together in his company Konfirm, with which he is eager to stimulate entrepreneurs to invest in Africa by means of providing advice, training and coaching.
